Ladies of London - Season 2, Episode 7




The Cougar in the Room

Marissa must work to salvage her friendship with Caroline Fleming after insulting her for dating a younger man. Julie once again fulfills her reputation as "Loose Lips" Montagu when she hosts a shooting weekend for the girls. Caroline Stanbury struggles to remain emotionally stable while her Gift Library continues its downward spiral.
